{"tid":310674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【劉曉波肝癌】病情急轉直下 已停用抗癌藥","createTime":"2017-07-06T04:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T14:16:39.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1daaa3071b99336909ab1449917cfc5e83c4ba9b","tid":310674,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T04:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170706/large/1499313021_0a31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170706%2Flarge%2F1499313021_0a31.jpg&h=07be1f5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n患末期肝癌的諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波，正在瀋陽中國醫科大學第一附屬醫院治療，其家屬透露昨日劉的情況急轉直下，肝功能變差，承不了治療，目前已經停用所有中、西醫抗癌藥。<br />\n<br />\n家屬指出，醫生周一曾為劉曉波抽走1,000毫升腹部積水，情況稍為好轉，但昨日情況急轉直下，由解放軍八一醫院副院長、全軍腫瘤中心主任秦叔逵，及北京協和醫院肝膽外科主任醫師毛一雷率領的專家組，再次到瀋陽為劉曉波會診。會診後醫生認為劉曉波的病情發展太快，肝功能變差，所以決定暫停藥物治療。<br />\n另外，再有劉曉波的近照曝光，劉曉波與妻子劉霞站着對望的合照，劉比以前瘦弱。"},{"pid":"7660e41ca211aaec0051cdd55b3f44c58dcf787f","tid":310674,"uid":76115,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T04:05:55.000Z","msg":"謀殺成功"},{"pid":"ab779a1ef63962fedd6605a62db60257a358ec64","tid":310674,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T04:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6234ee20bddbcbe70db41c65b2767d22c5baef69","tid":310674,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T04:52:54.000Z","msg":"北韓 支那 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a19a6b82c7f36ca3cbf89a3e1955d38a98ecf3","tid":310674,"uid":56107,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T04:55:09.000Z","msg":"仲留係中國醫，唔死都變半殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf121db2e92b9f4b82f9f5e7c8d84094eb16321b","tid":310674,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T04:55:48.000Z","msg":"來生唔好再做支那人啦"},{"